# GPU and Shader Governance

## Scope
- Shader/kernel assets: `**/*.glsl`, `**/*.hlsl`, `**/*.wgsl`, `**/*.cu`, `**/*.cuh`, `**/*.metal`.

## Must
- Keep GPU resource lifetime and synchronization assumptions explicit.
- Validate shader/kernel changes with correctness and perf evidence.
- Record feature-level fallback or failure behavior for unsupported paths.
- Align shader input/output contracts with CPU-side schema and IDs.

## Must Not
- Do not ship silent CPU/GPU contract mismatch.
- Do not modify synchronization behavior without regression checks.

## Required Evidence
- GPU validation artifact (correctness + perf) for affected scenario set.
